    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/8b524a008ecebbafdaa024b922f8f3a4.avif?t=1768903859\" width=600 height=149 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《失物招领有限公司》</strong>是一款轻松愉快的点击寻物游戏。神明“梅龙”已经被世人遗忘了很久很久，而你——小鸭，作为梅龙新创办的快递公司的第一位员工身负重任！快来帮助小鸭寻找神秘的遗失之物并恢复梅龙往日的光辉！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/a1679a19f6b91ae98cd53c6ee3571079.poster.avif?t=1768903859\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/a1679a19f6b91ae98cd53c6ee3571079.webm?t=1768903859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/a1679a19f6b91ae98cd53c6ee3571079.mp4?t=1768903859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/b8bc993d0c3d8248dc4cb7ade0e7b80f.avif?t=1768903859\" width=600 height=118 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/a7897f274b4104e1f4c0f7925f2e53c9.avif?t=1768903859\" width=600 height=269 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入冒险吧！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一场精彩纷呈、令人振奋的旅程吧！见证古代势力之间史诗般的战斗，并且用你的行动影响未来。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>改变世界吧！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >努力寻找遗失的物品，赚取工资，吸引新的客户，并用定制的物品装扮属于你的办公室！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索无数神奇的地方吧！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《失物招领有限公司》的世界充满生命力和各种意想不到的事件。丰富多彩且活力四射的生活在此满溢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/c66ca003a7530586d5de60a0fed133ce.avif?t=1768903859\" width=600 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 奇妙兴奋的故事情节</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 拥有各种令人兴奋的场景及与之互动的广阔空间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 结识各种古灵精怪的朋友</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 激动人心的谜题和秘密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 各类收藏品和成就</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/7031f7cfbf6975e9f4451386aaee6ef4.poster.avif?t=1768903859\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/7031f7cfbf6975e9f4451386aaee6ef4.webm?t=1768903859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179510/extras/7031f7cfbf6975e9f4451386aaee6ef4.mp4?t=1768903859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
